Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:05.32,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Many things happened at a very rapid pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:10.82,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Having earned official permission from \Nthe crown prince and the temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I set off with my team of rowdy adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.72,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,to begin the process of exterminating \Nthe dangerous demons
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.11,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and demon beasts infesting Beast Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.97,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,For areas that were relatively safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,we brought human resources and supplies, \Ntwo things every poor village needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.30,Main,Will,0,0,0,,The village is within sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.88,Main,Caravan,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.94,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,A village with access to supplies \Nbecomes more productive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:38.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Even if it starts out in debt, \Nit should eventually make a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.47,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Tonio handled all that \Nwith remarkable skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:48.50,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It was also Tonio who funded our activities \Nby soliciting donations and contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:52.95,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I could go on to become the \Nhead of a trade company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.61,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Feel free to go big!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.44,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,When I do, I'll be counting on your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:02.43,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Officially, this is just a lone \Npriest doing charitable work,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.04,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,so no one gets offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:11.03,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Of course, that means I need to remain loyal \Nto the crown prince and the temple, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:22.14,Show_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1075,0)\blur2\pos(320,290)}The Faraway Paladin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:48.31,Main,Anna,0,0,0,,Will, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.03,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I appreciate the work all of you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:57.54,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Bishop Bagley assigned a few \Npriests to me, including Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.28,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,They're all experienced priests
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.95,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,who can use the blessing, \Nas well as lead ceremonies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,such as festivals and funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.04,Main,Anna,0,0,0,,Reystov's party should be \Nreturning soon, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.71,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,When we got reports about demons \Nor demon beasts appearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:17.33,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Reystov and the other adventurers \Nwould pursue them as a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:21.50,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Incredible... They were all killed \Nwith a single fatal blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.36,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,No wonder they call him the Penetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.94,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Can you do this to wyverns, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.33,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,If it's within range of my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.94,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I would intervene in any \Ndisputes between villagers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.22,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and try to help them settle \Nthings reasonably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:41.04,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning to do all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:45.11,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Well, once you've done it the \Nfirst time, you're kinda stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.37,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Word of my interventions spread,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.18,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and I was called to intervene \Nin other villages' disputes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.19,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,My sudden role as an arbitrator \Ngave me a lot more to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:57.39,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,And whenever I had to visit other \Nvillages for friendly purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.76,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,or had a message I wanted to get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.94,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Bee was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:30.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,And so we traveled back and forth across \NBeast Woods, time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.63,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Mom, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,The atmosphere has changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.07,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,This area is relatively safe now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.40,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,so there's more merchant traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.87,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,A village that once had such \Na dark cloud hanging over it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.88,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,was now full of life and smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.82,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Gus, I finally understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.07,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,Money drives this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.94,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,With the power of money, you can \Nsolve anything without magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.54,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,You can buy the necessary \Ntools, hire people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:14.62,Flashback,Gus,0,0,0,,The ability to make a quick profit \Nis just as important as magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:19.26,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Everything you taught me was exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.82,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Making people smile and giving them hope
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,is more magical than actual magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.93,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.92,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Just as we were feeling the first \Nsigns of summer approaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:37.63,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.86,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:43.07,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Pip's party went west on recon, \Nand they're not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.31,Main,Will,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:47.88,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,They were planning to spend no \Nmore than ten days investigating,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.77,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,but it's two days past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.44,Main,Will,0,0,0,,So Pip and his party...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.31,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,They're talented guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.43,Main,Will,0,0,0,,All right. We'll go and search for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:00.64,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You, Menel, and I are \Ndefinitely going, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:06.06,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Could you put together two parties of \Npeople who excel in forest exploration?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.91,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,I'll get them together right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.92,Main,Will,0,0,0,,There's a chance that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.74,Main,Will,0,0,0,,they didn't simply get lost, \Nbut wound up in the demons' base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.69,Main,Will,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.30,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,There'll be a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.11,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.82,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Frankly, given the skills \NPip and his buddies have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.96,Main,Will,0,0,0,,it's hard to believe they just got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.61,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,So you think it was demons, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.44,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I think there's a good chance it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:39.67,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If we beat them, \Nthings'll settle down a bit here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.68,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I just hope they're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.79,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.98,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I guess I should say... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:51.22,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Uh... For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.98,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,A lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:57.29,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for you, \NI would've sunk as low as I could sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:07:02.62,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you that I'm here now, \Nliving for a respectable reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.51,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,So... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.26,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.58,Main,Will,0,0,0,,No, I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.10,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I knew nothing of the world, \Nand you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.83,Main,Will,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.24,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.87,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You could look at me and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.21,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.56,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,It's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.15,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What kind of demon beast made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.28,Main,AdventurerB,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.60,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,It's even bigger than a manticore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.27,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,A stray living in the valley... or...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.89,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,Well, they died fighting a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:04.03,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,Pip, Harvey, and Brennan must \Nbe pretty happy with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:06.17,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,but pretty pissed off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.51,Main,AdventurerE,0,0,0,,Yeah, like, "We didn't get to kill it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.48,Main,AdventurerF,0,0,0,,They died a good death, \Nworthy of adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.06,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,G'wan, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.24,Main,AdventurerE,0,0,0,,Virtuous gods, grant their souls rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.19,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Gracefeel, goddess of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.82,Main,Will,0,0,0,,please grant them peace and guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.24,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,There's a head missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:30.03,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,The damage is so bad, \Nit's hard to tell, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.86,Main,AdventurerB,0,0,0,,It probably got eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.25,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.37,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:39.07,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,He tossed all his gear as he ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.08,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,Why go deeper into the valley, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.18,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,If the path to the forest is blocked, \Nthis valley's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:46.40,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,He had no choice but to run deeper down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.05,Main,AdventurerB,0,0,0,,I guess that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.71,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:05.77,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.01,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,It's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.26,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,What's not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.84,Main,Will,0,0,0,,The footing in this valley is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.28,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Even if they fled, getting this far would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:19.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.19,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.17,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.99,Main,AdventurerF,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:28.80,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.67,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Stay calm! Keep your backs to the rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.81,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,Don't panic! Form a shield wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.17,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,We have to break through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:42.62,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It'll be fine! We should be \Nable to handle these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.22,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.11,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.05,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll give us a boost with \Nmagic and the blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:54.08,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Goddess of flux, repel the \Npoisons that rain down upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.04,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Fortis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:54.82,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Strong
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.32,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Life to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.32,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Vita ut Omnis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.20,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}All
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.52,Main,AdventurerB,0,0,0,,Much appreciated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.69,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.76,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gnomes, O gnomes, guardians of treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.38,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,link to form a stronghold \Nagainst our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.10,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Sylphs, Sylphs, maidens of wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.45,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,send your winds of protection \Nfor these brave warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.04,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,Much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:18.39,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Now, let's show these beasts who \Nthink they've trapped us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.89,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,which of us is really the prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.55,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.82,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:53.42,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.54,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gnomes, O gnomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.78,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,gather to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Build a fortress and surround with fences!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.17,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If he can just buy me time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.15,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.14,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.33,Words,Text,0,0,0,,Thunder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.34,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Tonit—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.01,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It cut my Words short!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:34.97,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.87,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,He misfired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.58,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.49,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Everything was going so well up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.15,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:50.11,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Where did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.46,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.07,Main - Top,Reystov,0,0,0,,William!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.05,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The techniques that I had honed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.54,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The spirit that I had refined...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:24.31,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The tactics that I had accumulated...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.13,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,None of it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.53,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,All I could rely on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:34.26,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,was blind fury and the abilities \Nof my demonblade as I hacked away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:42.27,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,in an ugly, unsightly battle \Nthat made me want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.80,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I felt I had wronged the three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.20,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I felt pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.30,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Stop! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.25,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Go heal Meneldor, quick! He's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.83,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.46,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Gracefeel, goddess of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.29,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Shine this healthy soul's light
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.10,Main,Will,0,0,0,,upon these wicked wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.20,Main,Will,0,0,0,,and banish these shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.72,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.74,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:56.01,Main,Will,0,0,0,,No! Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.47,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,My head feels fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:01.68,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Because I used the demonblade's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:08.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,But... I have to heal Menel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:15.95,Episode_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,2000)\pos(489,280)\blur1}Episode 11\N{\fscx90\fscy120}Valley of Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:11.51,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,William!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:12.51,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.63,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.57,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.96,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,A village not far from that valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:43.62,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,After that battle, we retreated with \Nyou and Meneldor on our backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.60,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,The chimera fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:48.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I se—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.32,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Where's Menel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.93,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.19,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Between the magic and protection \Nyou put on him before the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.66,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,and Meneldor's own quick retreat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.92,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,it seems like your blessing \Nwas just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.11,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,He hasn't woken up yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.92,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Then, I have to go to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:11.17,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,You need to rest a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.67,Main,Will,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:15.34,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Meneldor's condition is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:16.92,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,He's had all the care he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.82,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,You burned up too much strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.47,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,So rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.96,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Where did I screw up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,When I left Menel to handle the chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.15,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.70,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Given the circumstances, \NI didn't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.33,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Then, when was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Was it getting caught in that \Ntrap in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.48,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If I had been more careful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.86,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and taken the time to send out \Nscouts in all directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:59.66,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,we wouldn't have wandered \Nblindly into that valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.76,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,We had plenty of people, \Nwe'd been successful up to that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:08.97,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and we were rattled after \Nseeing some of our men dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,All of that led to a simple lack of caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:19.72,Main,Will,0,0,0,,No, I think I'm missing something... \Nsome fatal flaw...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.36,Main,MercenaryA,0,0,0,,Anyway, they retreated, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:25.08,Main,MercenaryB,0,0,0,,The Wyvern Killer and the Penetrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.60,Main,MercenaryC,0,0,0,,I heard they ran into some absurdly huge \Nmixed-up demon beast called a chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.13,Main,MercenaryA,0,0,0,,Wonder what they're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.52,Main,MercenaryC,0,0,0,,Also, that elf mix was hurt bad, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.95,Main,MercenaryA,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's really got it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:39.00,Main,MercenaryA,0,0,0,,When you're stuck with a monster \Nlike the Wyvern Killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.30,Main,MercenaryA,0,0,0,,no amount of lives is ever gonna be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.38,Main,MercenaryB,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.04,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah... I guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:58.58,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It wasn't my battle tactics that were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.83,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It was my estimation of our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.52,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I trusted Menel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.38,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I just believed that he'd have my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:10.51,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,that he could keep any \Nenemy in check for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.57,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I thought he could handle \Nthat much... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:19.29,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I came so close to getting Menel killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:23.82,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I just one-sidedly decided he was my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:28.17,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and in my innocent naïveté, \Nwithout even thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.60,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I put him up against dangers \Nhe wasn't ready for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.86,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.88,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Bee... Tonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.36,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,We got your message and rushed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:44.34,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Anna should arrive here \Nwith the priests later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.40,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:51.17,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will, we heard you saved Menel's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.26,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,You ran into a beast as \Nimpossibly tough as a chimera,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.70,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,but you still beat an insane \Nnumber of magic beasts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.62,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,and even saved Menel's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.42,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,You really are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:06.19,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I doubt Menel and the others who've \Nbeen stuck with me would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.08,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.62,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm going to check on Menel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.33,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.66,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Will, shouldn't you rest a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.02,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.93,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm very strong, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.03,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Ever since I left the city of the dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:34.42,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,people have constantly told me \Nthat in no uncertain terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:39.51,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Every time, I've just laughed \Nwryly and shrugged it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.65,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I think, subconsciously, I was \Ntrying not to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:48.09,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,But I can't avoid it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:54.29,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,In this world, \Nmy strength is beyond the pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.68,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,This is... my sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel... I'll fix you up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:22.49,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Gods, please take pity \Non Menel and heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.15,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Menel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:29.86,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I wanted a friend who could be my equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.30,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I wanted what the three of them had,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:35.08,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,comrades who had each other's backs, \Nsupported each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.16,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and respected each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.57,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,But maybe I was forcing that on you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.34,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,without even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.70,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I didn't want to acknowledge \Njust how strong I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.89,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If I did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.16,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If I set myself above everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.14,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and had to admit that I was different...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.40,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:03.98,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.04,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:10.27,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Oh... Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.44,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It was just that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I was afraid to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.91,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear not having \Nsomeone beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:23.94,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,That's why I tried to see the people \NI should have been protecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:28.08,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,should have been saving, as my equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:31.42,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I was averting my eyes from the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.90,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,when really, I was just scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,And for that despicable reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.17,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I almost killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.08,Main,Will,0,0,0,,But I finally get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I couldn't go on that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:57.86,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:00.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You're here because you're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.65,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Up until now, I was foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.83,Main,Will,0,0,0,,But everything is fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.72,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Please rest at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:11.84,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll put a stop to your sadness right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:15.60,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll save everything, \Neverything within my reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:20.96,Main,Will,0,0,0,,as your sword, and as your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.79,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll solve all of this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:31.71,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Will...
